{
  "_comment": "gmmff default theme. Structural tokens (fonts, spacing, radii) apply to both modes. Add a 'dark' and/or 'light' object to define per-mode color tokens. Any color key omitted from a mode block falls back to the top-level value. Omitting the mode block entirely falls back to the CSS defaults in app.css.",

